        "content": "<p>Here's what I did: <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/kbuzzard/e86eb3788caab340d5c40732de23d131\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://gist.github.com/kbuzzard/e86eb3788caab340d5c40732de23d131\">https://gist.github.com/kbuzzard/e86eb3788caab340d5c40732de23d131</a></p>",
